Package: jigsawR
Type: Package
Title: R Translations of JavaScript Jigsaw Puzzle Generators
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Philipp Thoss [aut, cre] (0000-0002-4672-2792)
Maintainer: Philipp Thoss <ph.thoss@gmx.de>
Authors@R: 
    person("Philipp", "Thoss", , "ph.thoss@gmx.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4672-2792"))
Description: R translations of Draradech's JavaScript jigsaw puzzle generators 
    with enhanced circular puzzle visualization capabilities. Supports both 
    rectangular and hexagonal/circular puzzles with high-quality SVG to PNG
    conversion and gradient backgrounds. Direct ports of the original JavaScript
    algorithms maintaining mathematical precision while adding R-based 
    visualization capabilities.
License: CC0
URL: https://github.com/pjt222/jigsawR
